text: Hilary Stacy Jaén Rodríguez (born 29 August 2002) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a defender for the Panama women's national team. ==International career== Jaén appeared in four matches for Panama at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Pan American Games competitors for Panama Category:Footballers at the 2019 Pan American Games
